OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRussian forces sharing base
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwith US troops in Niger    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Russian troops have been deployed to an
OL,6, airbase in Niger where American troops 
OL,7, are located, top US officials say.     
OL,9,FThe move is seen as adding pressure to 
OL,10,Fthe US as it negotiates withdrawing its
OL,11,Fforces from the country, following an  
OL,12,Fexpulsion order by its military junta. 
OL,14,FThe US has been operating two drone    
OL,15,Fbases in Niger, aimed at countering    
OL,16,FIslamic insurgents in the region.      
OL,18,FWashington has denounced last year's   
OL,19,Fcoup. In turn, junta leaders have      
OL,20,Fturned to Russia for assistance.       
